data.text: MS 2115/2 MS Short Title SIGRID UNDSET: NOGEN KVINDESAKS-BETRAGTNINGE Text SIGRID UNDSET: NOGEN KVINDESAKS-BETRAGTNINGE. - I ANL. PERKINS GILMAN: VERDEN SOM MANDEN HAR INDRETTET DEN Description MS in Norwegian on paper, London, October 1912, 16 ff., 26x20 cm, single column (20x16 cm), 23 lines in cursive script, autograph, signed. Provenance 1. Sigrid Undset, London (1912); 2. Samtiden, Oslo (1912-13); 3. Reidar Myhre, Oslo, 4. Norli's Antikvariat, Oslo. Published Essay in the periodical "Samtiden", 1912.
